summary:
Capital Change Notice Summary (Oceania Healthcare Limited)

  • Options Granted: 3,059,190 Options issued under Share Option Plan (10.6% of total outstanding Options).
  • Exercise Price: NZD $0.65 (based on 5-day VWAP prior to 26 May 2025).
  • Exercise Period: 10 business days after 2028 final results announcement, expiring 90 days later.
  • Settlement: Cashless (net-settled) exercise; shares issued based on market value vs. exercise price.
  • Purpose: Retention/performance alignment for CEO and employees.
  • Total Options Outstanding Post-Issue: 31,677,802.

No material liquidity, valuation, or capital structure impact identified (routine incentive issuance).

• Asset Sale Announcement: Spark New Zealand to sell 10% stake in HTAL to Hutchison Telecommunications (Amsterdam) BV.
  • Transaction Details:
  • Price: A$0.032/share (45% premium to upper end of Independent Expert valuation range).
  • Proceeds: NZ$47 million (to be used for net debt reduction).
  • Strategic Rationale: Divestment aligns with Spark’s review of non-core assets.

No additional material trading or capital markets information identified.

• Acquisition Announcement: Shift4 Payments, LLC to acquire Smartpay via Scheme of Arrangement at NZ$1.20/share (cash).
  • Premium: 46.5% to 90-day VWAP of NZ$0.82 (as of 20 June 2025).
  • Implied Equity Value: NZ$296.4M (A$274.1M).

  • EV/EBITDA: ~14.2x FY25 Normalised EBITDA (NZ$21.5M).

  • Conditions:

  • Shareholder, NZ High Court, and Overseas Investment Act approvals.

  • No financing condition; break fee/reverse break fee of NZ$2.96M each.

  • Key Dates:

  • Shareholder meeting: Q3 2025.

  • Expected implementation: Q4 2025.

  • Strategic Rationale:

  • Board unanimously recommends (subject to independent adviser validation).
  • 13.3% shareholder Microequities Asset Management supports.

No material information omitted.

• Drilling commenced at Bousquet Gold Project (Canada): Initial phase of 2,400m (10 holes) targeting high-grade Paquin Prospect (9m @ 16.96g/t Au) and Decoeur Prospect.
  • Approvals secured: Up to 38 drillholes (10,000m) permitted across priority targets.
  • Location: Project situated on Cadillac Break, a region hosting +110Moz Au deposits.

Note: No material financial/trading impacts (e.g., capital raises, timelines) identified.
